game.name: Cliff Diving
game.description:
Diving off the cliff can give many a reason to smile and make feel happy. Hey boys! The good news is that you do not need to go to the cliff to realize that fun. It might also be very risky and put your life at risk when you dare to do it in the real world. Why do not you join Cliff Diving online game to play the role of a fearless diver who can jump into the lagoon over and over again? The best part is that you can perform as many death-defying leaps as you can without getting injured in this brand new sports game.

When you click the play button, you would spot a beautiful cliff from where you have to jump right straight into the swimming pool.  Try to jump into the water in a straight position in this html5 performing game as this will help you to collect a bunch of money and create high score on the screen! You can also use this money to unlock new levels and increase your fun rate. Make sure that the funny-looking guy is able to jump from the cliff and turn quickly when he is the air and land with his head while reaching the water.

Try to make as many flips as you can to collect a significant amount of coins in this cool swimming game! Remember you land the wrong way on water, you are sure to lose your game immediately and you would have no choice, but to start it again. The fun-filled and relaxed atmosphere, beautiful beach landscape in the background, intuitive controls and simple gameplay will keep you entertained for hours. This summer-themed online game can be a nice choice to enjoy for players from all age groups, no download required.
